snippet.title: Send Help Director Sam Raimi Was Wowed By Rachel McAdams & Dylan O'Brien's Chemistry
snippet.description:
Send Help director Sam Raimi and producer Zainab Azizi discuss what they need on set with them, how they prepared the gross-out fluids intheir upcoming movie, and why Dylan O'Brien & Rachel McAdams work so well together.

Send Help arrives in theaters on January 30.
